{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, Vaira et al.",
    "(46) Farhadi Nia et al.",
    "10.3389/fdmed.2024.1456208 conducted a study in August 2023 to evaluate ChatGPT's accuracy in head and neck oral maxillofacial surgery, finding that 87.2% of the responses were accurate and 73% were comprehensive.",
    "Despite these promising results, researchers noted that ChatGPT is not fully reliable for decision-making in complex surgical cases.",
    "In prosthodontics, it is crucial to assess the accuracy and consistency of ChatGPT."
  ]
}